{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r732424907", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Beautiful decor and food but room for improvement", "diner_date": " December 2019", "rating_date": "13 December 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WWillow12", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r732424907-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We came here on a busy lunch time in December and was very impressed by the decor of the restaurant. As soon as you step inside you forget that you are in Canary Wharf.", "We sat upstairs which is very light and airy and I imagine this would also be very nice in the summer. Once seated it took around 20 minutes to take our drink and food orders and once we had ordered the waitress returned and told us two of the dishes we had ordered were unavailable. When asked to choose again we were told there were a total of four dishes not available on the menu which is slightly disappointing. ", "The food took quite some time to arrive and we didn't start eating until almost an hour after sitting down but the food was delicious. Portion sizes are small so you will most likely need sides with any main but all food was cooked perfectly.", "I was expecting more from this restaurant in terms of the overall service and experience but will certainly return and hope we just came on an off day."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r729180927", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Very average veggie breakfast", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "27 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "364shaung", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r729180927-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went here with a colleague for a mid week breakfast. Service was attentive, and the place as ever looked impressive. But the food was a little disappointing. My veggie breakfast was uninspired: watery beans, undercooked tomatoes, cold toast. Very overpriced at \u00a313.50. Over all, a little disappointed."]}
