{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r726130041", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food and great service...", "diner_date": " November 2019", "rating_date": "13 November 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Dream10855773329", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r726130041-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had booked a Sunday brunch for a family get together and had got there just after opening (11am). We were met with a smile, relieved of our cloaks and show efficiently to our table.", "We were a party of 8 plus a baby. The restaurant was totally baby friendly with a number of the excellent staff waving and amusing my grand daughter every time they passed.", "Food was great; most of us had a variation on Eggs Benedict and it was terrific. Not inexpensive but not overpriced compared to many of the establishments in the West end / Canary Wharf areas; definitely worth it and will go again."]}
