{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r720075175", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Average food. Overpriced tiny soft drinks. \u00a34.22 for 200ml of Coke ", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "21 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jetboy_uk", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "53"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r720075175-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I expected to receive better than average food from this restaurant, but it\u2019s on a par with TGI Fridays. The decor is nice, the staff were very polite but the food is not worth the money. ", "The biggest joke is they sell spirit mixer size cokes at full price. 200ml bottles are \u00a33.75 + 12.5% service. \u00a34.22 for a gulp of coke & a glass of ice. Coke is as expensive as beer. It\u2019s a rip off, if you order a coke in a bottle, it should be 330ml. ", "I will not be back for overpriced drinks & average food. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r720902113", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent breakfast ", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "24 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "O6824WYmiker", "reviewer_origin": ["Hornchurch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "561"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "140"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r720902113-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited for breakfast in October for a group of 12 people. Extremely friendly and helpful staff and had a table on the first floor overlooking the garden / mini park. Good range on the menu and reasonably priced. Service was excellent. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r721414671", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great breakfast", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "26 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Y8689CIdebbiew", "reviewer_origin": ["Reigate, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "499"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "156"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r721414671-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This place is huge and was concerned that it could be pretty hectic at breakfast - not at all! Only the downstairs is really occupied and it\u2019s all nicely spaced out tables.", "The food was great - all of us were pleased . I had slight food envy from the avo on toast that someone had but wasn\u2019t disappointed at all in my own choice. ", "Would definitely book again "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r714093110", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Always best choice ", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "30 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GoshGT", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r714093110-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We back again to the Ivy to celebrate my dad birthday. The service and food never disappoints us. Just perfect. Great and warm atmosphere in the first floor during brunch time. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r713846005", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Should have gone to Starbucks", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "29 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mile-Enders", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "86"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r713846005-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Lots of nice staff, not too busy when we went for breakfast, but had a long wait for everything. Coffee was lukewarm and sent it back. Toast was dry and over cooked. Side of bacon only arrived after asking twice where it was. Another long wait for pastries....", "Manager was apologetic and gave us a discount but will not be eating here again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r711881060", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great service and ambience.", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "22 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Clademc", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "26"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r711881060-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came for a friends birthday meal and the service was fantastic.", "The barman had a great knowledge of the drinks and the waiter, who was really", "Young, was knowledgable and really attentive and polite.", "I ordered the chicken Milanese which wasn\u2019t great (I asked for a recommendation and in fairness to the waiter he recommended other dishes that I just didn\u2019t fancy at the time). I wasn\u2019t that impressed with the chicken, it was nothing spectacular; the arracini was lovely, the spinach in cream was ok a bit sloppy and rich, The sweet potatoes again were ok but not bursting with flavour.", "It hasn\u2019t put me off because it was a lovely atmosphere and I think I need to order something else rather than play it safe with the chicken. ", "I would definitely recommend and unlike me take up the recommendations from the waiters! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r715565943", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Sorry, but I don\u2019t do mice", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "5 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "toptripper186338", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "60"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r715565943-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went early evening, started with the shellfish cocktail, which was ok. Partner had the scallops, three that is.The mains: veal fine, but Chicken Milanese dry, regardless of the runny fried egg. Sides: chips great, but mash potatoes, although served with melted butter, were cold. By the time the server came over to check our meal I had already ate most of my main, so an offer to reheat the mash was too late. We were offered a complimentary coffee, but unfortunately my husband spotted a mouse running around on the terrace, where minutes earlier diners had sat. I have a rodent phobia so we asked for the bill. We discreetly told the waiter about the mouse, and was assured by ", "the maitreD that pest control was dealing with the problem, but as the restaurant was situated on the green, it was to be expected. We arrived at 5pm, service started at 5. 17 and we left at 18.08. It was a very short, and disappointing birthday celebration."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r712042032", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Don't miss out on the Arancini", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "22 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ad1402", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "13"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r712042032-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The Ivy is a good option for brunch; we had eggs royale as well as eggs benedict, the latter missing a bit of salt and which could have had slightly more hollandaise sauce. Although a bit pricy compared to similar venues, those dishes are accompanied with fries, which is a plus! The highlight was the taste of the arancini, which were lovely. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r714222309", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful experience", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "30 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Mary9B", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r714222309-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great attentive service, delicious food, cocktails are just amazing, specially Salted caramel expresso martini. It was so professional touch with congratulations plaque for our special occasion. Just good vibes and pretty atmosphere. Will go there again and again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r714248475", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place ", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "30 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "D447", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r714248475-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Enjoyable family lunch again. Can\u2019t fault the place, service and staff. Very good Gin selection. ", "Suggestion: add more choices of craft beers. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r715189364", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A pleasant change", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "4 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "david j", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "66"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "27"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r715189364-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["visited last Saturday for lunch at 2pm so arrived at 1 to be seated at the bar which serves really clean fresh drinks, a great bar, great bar staff. After being seated in the all day restaurant we were offered 2 menus one of which was vegetarian, a pleasant change and great selection. The waiting staff were excellent and very professional, this restaurant should make the others in Canary Wharf sit up as its head and shoulders above most if not all. I hope they keep up the standards."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r714845540", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great experience with good food and ambience ", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "2 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "laj2e7", "reviewer_origin": ["Orlando, Florida"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "818"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "168"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r714845540-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Located in Canary Wharf, this restaurant was a perfect cap to the day . It had lots of windows overlooking the lawn with an eclectic British decor . The seating was comfortable which lenses itself to a night of fun and fellowship . The service was professional and efficient . We had the vegetable and real Shepherds pie . Both were delicious and served with Sauce . The fresh vegetables were prepared perfectly as an accompaniment . The bar service was the only slow service of the night . The desserts were spectacular . Overall a delightful experience . "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r714555399", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Quick lunch visit was very good", "diner_date": " October 2019", "rating_date": "1 October 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "RJB1000", "reviewer_origin": ["UK"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "211"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "170"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r714555399-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came in today for lunch with an ex colleague and to be fair it was very good, I had the salmon fishcake with a side and it couldn't be faulted.", "The service was equally very good.", "It can be noisy when it's busy but I'd definitely return, the Ivy team did a great job today."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r711367965", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Hospitality at its finest!!", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "20 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "alexandrosk405", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "6"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r711367965-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I have been working in Canary since 2017 and I have to say that The Ivy in The Park is the most well-structured restaurant in the area. Interior design, relaxing vibes, great atmosphere in combination with the outstanding service that I received made me feel so welcome. Genuine conversations with our main waiter, the manager made us feel like we knew each other for years. Excellent European food with plenty of options ,fantastic cocktails. It's a must, will definitely visit again and again again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r707243172", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointed ", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "6 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Crab_Hunting_Girl", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "64"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r707243172-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Let me start by saying this restaurant has a great atmosphere. The decor is beautiful and it has a very positive energy. The ginger beer is refreshing, and I highly recommend it. But that's where the positives stop. The service was slow and lackluster. The food was average at best. I definitely expected more from an Ivy restaurant. In my opinion, it did not live up to the Ivy standard. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r708060493", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "A surprise afternoon tea that turned into not so much of a surprise!", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "9 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rubyjune1992", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r708060493-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I had my mothers 50th birthday celebrations at The Ivy on Saturday, the booking was at 3.30 pm for 12 people. I have been to their restaurants loads of times so thought it would be the perfect venue for a surprise afternoon tea. The tea was lovely and the men who served us were great and helpful.", "The issue is I called up that morning to let them specifically know this was a surprise afternoon tea for my mums 50th so she had no idea about her friends and family being there, I asked if they could make a note and let reception know and I was assured this would be done and made a note of so nobody said anything when we arrived to give it away.", "When we arrived at The Ivy and I told them my name the woman on reception said 'oh yes I think your other guests are here'. I tried covering this up and saying oh no there are no other guests but it was too late my mum had already heard and asked questions so she knew.", "I know this would have been an accident but the fact I called to mention beforehand and then my mums surprise was totally ruined is a real shame and I expected better from such a well known brand and restaurant."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r708069748", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Birthday Lunch ", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "9 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jeni007", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "32"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r708069748-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had a birthday lunch with my husband. The food and service was excellent. I thought it was going to really expensive it was reasonable. ", "It was a warm day we sat upstairs which is partly open which was lovely. ", "I will be returning."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r709299263", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Attention to Detail", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "13 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "philip m", "reviewer_origin": ["Gainsborough, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "120"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r709299263-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["What a pleasure to find this eatery. Felt totally looked after, even though we only ordered tonic water and one food course each. Noteworthy attention to detail. Menu is interesting. I had the Monkfish and Prawn Curry, brilliant. ", "Found it hard to locate, good landmark is Waitrose, The Ivy is in the park opposite."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r707942091", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "Disappointing to say the least", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "8 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "brad7roberts", "reviewer_origin": ["Glasgow, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r707942091-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Plenty of staff doing the rounds - none seemingly doing anything. 15 mins to take first drink order on a reserved table, in a what looked to be half full restaurant. Both main courses removed from bill as inedible (burger far too charred and cut up as if to check readiness? Sea Bass same overpowering charred flavour?). ", "Ultimately a disappointing visit. Wouldn\u2019t go again. One good is they made a very good cocktail off-menu, but that did not restore faith in The Ivy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r710267259", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best of the Ivy Collection!", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "16 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AgataM455", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r710267259-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I wandered in with a friend of mine for a quick Sunday brunch, and was immediately greeted by friendly receptionists and incredible decor. We have been showed to the cute table in the garden area. We have started with some zucchini and arancini, then followed with eggs benedict and royale that exceeded our expectations and are definitely best in town! All of this accompanied by their excellent selection of drinks. The icing on the cake was their salted caramel espresso martini so make sure you try it! Can\u2019t recommend enough!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r710336350", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner", "diner_date": " September 2019", "rating_date": "16 September 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AminaPM", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r710336350-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came to celebrate my job promotion with work friends and from the time I entered the Ivy to the last step out it was amazing!! From start to end we had the most welcoming and polite waiter/waitress- I have to mention Alex and Marianne who firstly didn\u2019t let our glasses go empty and secondly, Alex provided us with top entertainment as well as perfect hospitality! I\u2019m so happy Vanessa introduced the Ivy to us and made us have such a great time! ", "The venue is so pretty and a great vibe. The food is just as nice! We especially loved the desserts-Totally recommend it :)"]}
