{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r695504103", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Catch up with Friends", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "4 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "cherryt1939", "reviewer_origin": ["Upshire, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "62"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r695504103-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I went for lunch her with 3 friends for a long overdue catch up. Very good food and service. In particular, the prawn and monkfish curry, followed by baked Alaska. Our waitress was informative and made recommendations when asked but didn\u2019t hurry us, while we caught up and admired the views over the green. We sat upstairs but inside, with the doors open so not in the direct sunlight, had a G&T and watched the world go by. ", "I will return. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r695824290", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Celebratory lunch. ", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "5 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "769fleurw", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r695824290-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Sunday afternoon lunch for 3 for a celebration. We hadn\u2019t booked but this was not a problem. We were seated outside with a view of the screen in the park showing the cricket. This was my second visit, service was impeccable, food delicious especially the puddings. Happy tummies all round. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r695424934", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Just give it a miss", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "4 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Karen L", "reviewer_origin": ["Leeds, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "59"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r695424934-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Met a colleague here for meal after work. Place was very busy but we were seated quickly with reservation. There was live music on outside which made it noisy but was already very noisy inside, not too much of a problem. Wasn\u2019t tempted much by menu but ordered steak, medium rare, it came grey and cold and very over cooked. Sides came a while after, also over cooked. My pet hate - the waiters keeping wine off the table which only works if the service is very good, and it wasn\u2019t, so we ended up waiting and asking for wine every time, until I asked for them to just leave it on table. Slow service (not their fault, just very busy and not enough staff, they were all pleasant) pretty poor food, and over priced. Ivy obviously trying to sweat its brand and doing so very badly. Would not go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r696641647", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointed ", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "7 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "feelinghungry99", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "71"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "29"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r696641647-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As a big fan of The Ivy, and having visited some of the other new Ivy, we decided to give this a try after a spot of shopping.", "Sadly, we were disappointed. The restaurant was very noisy, the service poor and the food average. In fact it appeared that many of the staff didn't want to be there - miserable faces, rolling of eyes and unprofessional comments were all part and parcel of our experience. It almost seemed as if there was something going on which was causing an undercurrent of discontent amongst the staff. The young lady who served us was pleasant enough but seemed rushed off her feet, consequently our service was slow, whilst groups of other staff 'lounged' around - some actually leaning against walls chatting. Not what I have come to expect from this chain and I won't recommend or return to this particular branch. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r695851216", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Beautiful decor, excellent location & efficient staff", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "5 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gunjan S", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "51"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r695851216-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The restaurant is in a good location in Canary Wharf, especially if you're visiting in the summer. I really liked the decor - very extravagant and 'over the top' (in a nice way).", "The restaurant was very busy and I imagine a reservation is advised if visiting in the evenings. Despite how busy it was, I found the staff to be very quick in taking orders but also keeping the balance of not interrupting you constantly. ", "The menu isn't very extensive but the food is good. IMO the best thing about this restaurant is the location and the atmosphere."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r689401205", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Loved it", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "14 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Rissacsw", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "119"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "58"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r689401205-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited here with my friend and her daughter and after walking around trying to find somewhere for 30 mins we came across the ivy. We never had a booking but was found a table straight away. It was very busy as it was a Saturday afternoon but the service was great. The food was lovely and very reasonably priced. I will defo return in the future"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r683877205", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "An incredible experience", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "24 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "soyRyco", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r683877205-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We have booked a table with a friend of mine whom I haven't seen in 10 years to catch up and to talk about business somehow the manager Gloria got wind of this and pretty much personally looked after us. we had the most amazing food I have had in a long long time the service was second to none. all the waiters and waitresses really looked after us for instance when the filtered table water was running low without asking and a new filled up bottle was already on the table. Furthermore after we enjoyed our delicious meal we've being given a special treat which was absolutely unique it is a very nice restaurant in a great location with very friendly staff and since the manager personally looked after us it was an experience made in heaven. I highly recommend this place and I'm very glad to return anytime."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r696278471", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Not value for money ", "diner_date": " August 2019", "rating_date": "6 August 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "collins873", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "37"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r696278471-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The service was friendly and helpful. I can't deny that. Prices are not value for money. There is no main dish below approx 18 pounds (Not talking about pies or vegetarian meals). You need to add a side dish of approx 5 pounds. Then desserts which are around 8 pounds. Then a drink. You end up with 35-40 pounds per person plus the service charge. Simply not worth it because we stayed hungry even after the dinner. Fish dishes are so small. Lobster linguine is the biggest steal. A plate of macaroni with 100g of lobster, 30 pounds. Oh please. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r684294932", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Disappointing lunch today I'm afraid", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "25 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "deborahl130371", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "75"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "15"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "30", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r684294932-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was here for a lunch with 3 friends. Our waiter was lovely, very attentive but sadly the 2 things I picked were dry and tasteless. I ordered the truffle arancini to start. They are small and were very dry but I was hungry so I ate them. I had asked for my burger to be medium rare and was told they do not do this any more......very surprised at this as I didn't ask for rare. I said as long as it came pink that's fine but I did not want well done. Off he went and what came back, a well done tasteless and dry burger. I couldn't send it back because I was short on time and couldn't wait for something else! There is no excuse for it to be tasteless though in a restaurant like this. In addition to this when we arrived we got given a glass of champagne, very nice. I had 1 more then had to leave the group and get back to work. I was told by our waiter that he would take the champagne off the bill. I had noticed that there were 2 on there as well when I had only had 1 as the first one was complimentary. I now know it was left on so the girls had to pay for it. All in all a very disappointing visit!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r684327516", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely food really nice set up", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "25 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "worthy23", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "84"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r684327516-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I met my friend for lunch on Saturday. The service was very good. The atmosphere was nice, the decorations and view lovely.", "The food was delicate, thoughtful and tasty. The champagne cocktails where super nice. ", "We sat, ate and drunk in very relaxed environment, at leisure, we talked for 5 hours. We were not pushed out and they made us feel confortable. It was perfect. ", "I definitely want to go back. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r685491773", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent!", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "30 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "clds432", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "41"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r685491773-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We celebrated my birthday here for a Sunday brunch and it was perfect. Service is good and friendly and efficient. Good delicious. We had the crispy duck starter which was amazing as well as the freshly baked warm salt crusted sourdough bread. My husband had the ribeye steak and I had the salmon and asparagus- both excellent! For dessert passion fruit baked Alaska. We were outside on a gorgeous summer afternoon. Could not have been better. We will definitely return there soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r687259429", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Excellent food", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "6 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "chirags935", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "95"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "31"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r687259429-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited this place not knowing too much about what to expect. The food was delicious and on the whole the service was good although a tad slow at times. The lobster linguini was outstanding. I really enjoyed it."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r688643738", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Incredible", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "11 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "kirstycousins97", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r688643738-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited on May 17th with a couple of friends as a celebration. The atmosphere was wonderful, a really well decorated and vibrant space. ", "We were greeted promptly by our waitress (unfortunately I can\u2019t remember her name!) who was absolutely lovely. She was available throughout the meal, checking regularly if we needed anything else. ", "We skipped starters and went straight to mains. All of us enjoyed our food so much, a definite 10/10 all round. A couple of my friends dined off a separate menu which was filled with extra vegan and vegetarian options - a nice surprise for them as we didn\u2019t see this online! ", "I then had a white chocolate hot chocolate and a dessert (see photo!) which was delightful. ", "Nothing bad to say about this visit. Would come back in a heartbeat! Well done to everyone at The Ivy Canary Wharf"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r687454041", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great food, drink, service", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "7 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WotldTraveller", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "135"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "34"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r687454041-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Lunch on a sunny Friday. Bustling but not heaving. Great food - a friend said the best fish and chips he'd had in a long time - and drink (Seville Gin and Tonic and I'm told one - or two - of the best White Russians in ages). Friendly unfussed service. Very happy customers who will return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r687844099", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Book ahead! ", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "8 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sharesomephotos", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "403"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "162"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r687844099-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A relatively new addition to the plethora of dining establishments around Canada Square, The Ivy brings it's renowned stamp of British cuisine to the masses.", "Probably a good idea to book ahead, although we did manage to get a table on a late Sunday afternoon as a walk in. My favorite is the crispy duck salad followed by fish and chips, whilst my wife tucked into asparagus and lobster, followed by miso cod. Not the cheapest restaurant that you will ever eat at but the food is excellent and the service was very friendly.", "2 courses pp and a modest drink will set you back the best part of \u00a3100 inc VAT and service. Saying that, a pleasant dining experience, good for groups and I would go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r689318150", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Lovely brunch!", "diner_date": " July 2019", "rating_date": "13 July 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rhirani92", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "13"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "7"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r689318150-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Our visit to the Ivy was lovely! We managed to get a table in the terrace, on a busy Saturday morning for brunch. The food was great, would definitely recommend the pistachio and raspberry dessert. Also, our waiter, George, was very welcoming and provides great service. There was also a great atmosphere. Would I return to the Ivy in Canary Wharf? Of course! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r676545865", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Great food, wine & cocktails with lovely staff. Will return. ", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "26 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "PennyPurples", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "619"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "345"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r676545865-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["17 Jan: I enjoyed my weekday evening dinner here. They have a good selection of cocktails, friendly staff, a wide variety of food (something for everyone) and all our dishes were well cooked, tasty and generously portioned. Would happily return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r683601826", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Nice meal, nice staff", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "23 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jfd17101951", "reviewer_origin": ["Woodford, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "209"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "244"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r683601826-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was treated by our kids to dinner. The menu is decent and reasonably priced for London. The kids had been here before so were bursting with suggestions. Danielle has a severe nut allergy so we checked with the staff who were very good indeed (some places just think that it isn't too important). They do a craft pale ale which is very nice indeed and a craft lager which Dave enjoyed. The girls had a bottle of prosecco.", "The wine list is a bit pricy with prosecco at \u00a342 but perhaps its just that I don't eat in London often.", "The arancini balls were good and the matchstick thin zucchini was brilliant. Dave and I had the tempura prawns and they were excellent. We also had the smoked salmon, which was a little salty.", "Jean had the shepherd's pie and Dave and I had the monkfish curry. The curry was fabulous. Danielle tried the black miso cod and was so impressed she gave us all a taste and now wants me to cook it at home.", "All in all a lovely evening and well worth a return visit."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r676829652", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "1st class!!!", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "27 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "stants01", "reviewer_origin": ["Amsterdam, The Netherlands"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r676829652-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great food! Great price! Great ambiance! But best of all..... our waiter.... Filippoi, this guy was AMAZING! I eat in a lot of high end restaurants and this was some of the best, genuine, attentive service I have ever had! Gold star!!! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r678743393", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Not approved! - Things to improve", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "4 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Princygirl", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "209"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "81"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "30", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r678743393-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Met a friend of mine here and she reserved a table for dinning on the terrace!", "I have arrived before her and when I mentioned her name they asked me \"dining yes?\" and I said \"no, we are not having dinner!\" and so they cancelled her booking and moved me inside because outside is apparently just for dining. ", "Let me start from the beginning. ", "This place is aesthetically lovely, I got so excited when they opened the Ivy in Canary Wharf! I've been wanting to try it for quite some time now, and i got the opportunity with my friend. ", "I do not think is a smart way of organising the space by \"if you proper eat with us and spend a lot of money, then you can eat outside!\" if you don't expect to eat (people can change their mind by any chance?) then you sit inside. This for me is a terrible way of doing business. ", " ", "Why not creating an outside space for people who are not planning right at that moment to order food; and an allocated space for people who actually want to have lunch/dinner there? ", "Now.. I wonder if I ordered a 5k bottle of wine but I don't want to sit inside - what would you guys do? This should improve, especially as there is people with money coming to your place and leave big tips!", "In addition, I confirm as some reviews mentioned here, that the staff is not very smiley or engaging a lot! I felt (but again it might be just me) that they had some kind of attitude in certain situation! ", "Would I go back? Yes, but I hope it gets better. ", "Value: 7"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r677301335", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Solid Eatery", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "29 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "C2760XTstuarth", "reviewer_origin": ["Nottingham, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r677301335-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As i sometimes work from the Thomson Reuters offices in Canary Wharf, I end up staring at this restaurant from the break room.", "From a distance and up close it's a very interesting looking building within an oddly green area of the Wharf, I was hoping for good weather so I could enjoy their extensive outdoor seating but the UK weather intervened so we ended up indoors.", "Front of house good, whisked to table upstairs in short order even though we turned up 20 minutes early. Asked for drinks and food order to be taken later, no issues with that. ", "Put in a table for 2 next to the window, good view, just be aware that it can be a little cold next to the glass. Be wary of this in winter but they do have overhead heaters.", "Wine list decent, prices London standard but you don't need to spend mega bucks on a bottle as some of the cheaper options were decent (according to Vivino analysis).", "Settled on a couple of glasses of English sparking which were good and some US Zin which was very drinkable along with an order of truffle arancini which was cracking.", "Starter:prawn and lobster cocktail, fresh tasting, good sauce, maybe actually a little too big but it sounds odd to complain about that.", "Main: Iberico pork chop, cracking piece of meat, maybe some of the best pork I've had.", "Dessert: Apple Tart, not bad, decent portion size but felt like there was something missing.", "Cost: \u00a3200 including service charge, 2 people, 3 courses each, 1 bottle wine,fizz each to start and glass of wine at the end.", "All in all, a good visit to the upmarket chain. No drama, plenty of staff and service was good. Would be more than happy to return."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r681332769", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Delectable!!!!!", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "13 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Beerwolf4", "reviewer_origin": ["Burlington, Canada"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "92"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "37"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r681332769-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A very nice restaurant in Canary Wharf...great atmosphere with excellent food! The Tempura Prawns and the Steak Tartare were excellent...3 of us had different mains and all were great!!!! For a place like this, the prices were reasonable."]}
