{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r681483360", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Second time around - pefection!", "diner_date": " June 2019", "rating_date": "14 June 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "elsiezeh", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "5"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r681483360-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["From the moment we arrived, we knew this would be special. Lovely spot to view the large screen outside, exceptionally courteous waiting staff, beautifully presented food that tasted delicious. Fabulous time at this restaurant today. Thank you for listening and responding to feedback. I'll be back again and again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r672098955", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good but not perfect", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "7 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "johndriscolluk", "reviewer_origin": ["Petts Wood, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "172"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "102"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r672098955-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the restaurant over the Bank Holiday weekend.", "The Wharf was reasonably quiet as one would expect but the restaurant was extremely busy which is always a good sign.", "The food was great. I had the rib eye steak with sides of Truffle and Parmesan chips, creamed spinach and green beans which I shared with my wife who went for the Chicken Milanese.", "For some reason, our table wasn't dressed with a white tablecloth like I would have expected for the Ivy. Maybe it was decor related as the round tables wasn't dressed yet the square tables were dressed? Who knows. Not a problem at all. I also grains of rice in with the Truffle and Parmesan chips. That stood out like a sore thumb to me. The restaurant was busy but there was no way that should have happened. I didn't sent it back as it wasn't a major issue (and I was hungry and didn't want further delay to my food!)", "The food was great though. The chocolate bombe desert was quite possibly my favourite desert for a very very long time. It was exceptional. I'd come back to the Ivy purely for that desert alone.", "Parents of babies be warned. Although there are baby change facilities, there is very little room between tables for a buggy. When we made our booking, we indicated that we would be bringing our month old daughter with us, so we was accommodated for but be aware that if you turn up unannounced then you may run into difficulties.", "Good value for money based on the standard of food to price paid. With my wife working on the Canary Wharf estate, this restaurant will be on our list of go to's for the foreseeable future."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r672773208", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Service without a smile", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "9 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Z4007QQneilr", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r672773208-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I\u2019ve been a regular at the original Ivy for many years but I have stopped going since they renovated because it\u2019s too noisy and lacks privacy, but the service is always excellent and the regular waitering staff are cheerful, happy and friendly. ", "The new branch in Canary Wharf is nicely decorated and the food standard Ivy fair i.e. very good but routine. You also don\u2019t have to make small talk with the tourists at the next table like you now have to do in the restaurant in town. ", "However the staff are all unfriendly, unwelcoming and surly and although efficient it was obvious that this is not a well managed restaurant where people want to work and enjoy their jobs despite the huge tips they are all getting. I did not see a single member of staff crack a smile the entire evening. ", "It makes for an unpleasant atmosphere and leaves you with a poor impression of the restaurant. ", "Also, which fool designed the washrooms? One mens toilet for a 200 seat restaurant?...my main course was served while I queued for 15 minutes and I sent it back because it was cold. Very basic errors in planning and lack of staff training. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r672221852", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing!!!", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "7 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Gem A", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "15"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "11"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r672221852-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Loved this IVY! Very impressive. Booked a table 10mins before we arrived but it was so lovely and quiet. Service is excellent, food spectacular. Well worth it. Will definitely return. And very reasonable prices. Overall very very happy and impressed with everything. Great job guys."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r676411484", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "110%", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "25 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "johnweedon1", "reviewer_origin": ["San Cayetano, Spain"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "77"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "22"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r676411484-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great Restaurant in the centre of Canary Wharf. Staff there offer fantastic service, food great, great surroundings. Competitive prices. Give them a try, very close to the Jubilee Line."]}
