{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r672835351", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Dinner at the bar", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "9 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "KrissyMilw", "reviewer_origin": ["Hanson, Massachusetts"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "49"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r672835351-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I was in London for work by myself, so always nice when dining solo to eat at the bar. I had seared seared tuna, which was great. The service at the bar was exceptional, very friendly and attentive staff. I was there on a Thursday evening after work."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r674600619", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Faultless", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "17 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Screech96", "reviewer_origin": ["Minehead, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r674600619-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["An absolutely pleasurable experience in this exquisite restaurant. My friend and I recently visited the restaurant on a whim after looking for somewhere to have our evening meal whilst on our annual trip to the big smoke. Boy - I'm so glad we chose the Ivy in the Park!", "Everything was perfect. Without a doubt, one of the best Fish and Chips I have tasted! The extensive menu of eloquent drinks and first-class dishes, coupled with the friendly service, made this one of my favourite eatery's I've ever had the fortune to sit inside.", "WILL COME BACK!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r674354627", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Terrible service and hair in chocolate bomb", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "16 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Ellelouisa27", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["20", "20", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r674354627-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Came for a celebratory work lunch.", "The lady at the desk didn't have our booking and continued to call us by the wrong name. I asked for truffle chips and was willing to pay extra as I had these at Ivy in Bath and loved them but the waiter said he would ask chef and let me know. He clearly didn't as 30 mins later my burger arrived with plain chips.", "Ordered desert and was giving a chocolate bomb with a hair in it, sent it back as soon as it came and a new one came back 15 mins later so I had to eat it on my own after my colleagues had finished theirs. I love The Ivy and had a great experience in Bath but wouldn't return back to CW one - it's a shame as I work literally next door."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r674628462", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Absolutely Fab!!!", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "17 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GoshGT", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r674628462-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Absolutely love this place!! Deco, service, staff and food first class. Had a great late brunch on Saturday. Staff were friendly and very knowledgeable with my food request. We asked for special cocktail which was not on the menu, bartender accommodated all requests even came to the table to explain how he would prepare the drink. Lovely atmosphere with life music downstairs. ", "Will back again!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r675515446", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "An object lesson in dinner service", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "21 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Chris G", "reviewer_origin": ["Johannesburg, South Africa"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "131"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "57"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r675515446-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Wonderful venue in a little park in Canada Square, not far from Canary Wharf DLR and Underground stations. We had a couple of relaxed G&Ts before moving to our table. The restaurant was jam-packed and there was a wonderful vibe. We started with the Belgian endive salad and I had the chicken Milanese with half chips, half spinach. All washed down with a crisp rose. Service was excellent and friendly. Would heartily recommend this restaurant. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r671958087", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Celebrations in the perfect setting!", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "6 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ReviewedbyJonathan", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "57"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "14"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r671958087-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came here for a celebration dinner over the May Bank holiday with my partner and we had such a wonderful experience. We were seated upstairs by the window with a lovely view out to the terrace and square. Our waiters and waitresses were all amazingly attentive and completely charming which added to the whole experience. The food was delicious and the presentation matched this equally. Highly recommend this place for any occasion."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r666459159", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Oh fabulous place to eat", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "14 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Joey N", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "14"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r666459159-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Went for my wife\u2019s 50th Birthday lunch. Oh best place as staff friendly n relaxing. Nice cosy place", "Food is 10/10 as had the best shepherds pie ever. Highly recommend the dish. Good size pudding. Fab cocktails. Wife had a little birthday cake with candle. It was amazing. Want to try the afternoon tea there soon."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r667850565", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great place for brunch", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "20 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jen400", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "8"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r667850565-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["On a sunny Easter Saturday, sat out on the lower terrace, great setting with a view over the green. had a lovely brunch. Service was prompt and food arrived quickly. I had the eggs royale and my mum had the shepherds pie. Both looked stunning and tasted wonderful. Both were reasonably priced as well. Would definitely go back as the burgers,pancakes and dessert which all looked equally as yummy."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r666299098", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Just lovely", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "14 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Sazzle198428", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "46"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "38"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r666299098-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Attentive staff, lovely food and lovely atmosphere in restaurant. I enjoyed my crispy duck salad to start and I had fish and chips with mushy peas for main which was so yummy. Def recommend. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r668282582", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great Place for Brunch", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "22 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "johnBLondon", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r668282582-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to the Ivy for brunch during Easter weekend. The place is very pleasant and the food is very good. Service is excellent, our waitress Brigitta was very nice. ", "Seating outside was only available by booking in advance, so we would advice to plan your visit in advance. Definitely one of the best places for a brunch in Canary Wharf!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r666556650", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Sunday Lunch", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "15 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Chooch16", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r666556650-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just had a most enjoyable lunch at The Ivy, Canary Wharf. Food was excellent with a rum baba to die for preceded by one of their house cocktails. It was too cold to sit outside on one of the terraces, however it was sunny and the outlook from the upstairs dining area gave a real spring feeling to the family occasion."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r669084073", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "My new venue of choice in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "25 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "marcusp438", "reviewer_origin": ["Welwyn Garden City, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "211"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "49"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r669084073-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I regularly take clients out for lunch and have a few places I tend to use but considering there is so much choice this list is small. Boisdales and Roka have been good for years. But now I have just experienced The Ivy in the park.", "It was a Wednesday at 12.30 and was rammed so must be good", "A very small table for 2 but enough room and was not too loud so could easily talk", "Wine selection was very good and can recommend the Gavi.", "Started with the Duck salad which I wolfed down as so damn tasty", "Rather than my standard steak I opted for the Monkfish and prawn curry. well presented and I will have this again as was very good and light so a perfect lunch", "No doubt I will now be a regular so looking forward to getting to know the team", "Not cheap at \u00a3131 for 2 but was well worth it (wine was \u00a350)", "Enjoy"]}
