{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r671573026", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A very enjoyable experience!", "diner_date": " May 2019", "rating_date": "5 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Harninio", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "25"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r671573026-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A lovely late lunch in a very nice restaurant, we really enjoyed the meal which was tasty and well presented. Our waiter was super, very attentive and friendly. The location is quirky, right in the heart of Canary wharf, it's like a little bit of peace and quiet among the fast paced outside world!!!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r671945734", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Disappointing", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "6 May 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "v k", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "21"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r671945734-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited the restaurant for anniversary dinner and was really disappointed. Went there because it was close to office and had a vegetarian menu. Food was below average and expensive. To make it worst they forgot the soup and starters we ordered and straight away gave main course. Only good thing was the ambience. I wouldn\u2019t go there again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r661583051", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good option in Canary Wharf", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "27 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "joseaB565QB", "reviewer_origin": ["Porto, Portugal"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "177"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "46"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r661583051-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited to dinner.", "The environment is nice and the staff very kind.", "The menu has several options.", "The food was served quickly and it was delicious!", "We request steaks and monkfish curry and it were good options!", "It is a good not exceptional."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r662666582", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great ", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "1 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "GOMReviews", "reviewer_origin": ["Saffron Walden, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "47"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "25"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r662666582-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Five of us had lunch on Saturday and were super impressed with the food and service ", "Have been to the Ivy in Cambridge before so knew what to expect ", "Super location, great comfortable restaurant with super friends ", "Well worth a visit and would definitely return "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r662261185", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "As good as the original", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "30 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "TerryE107", "reviewer_origin": ["Croydon, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "313"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "235"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r662261185-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Called in on spec for brunch on a sunny day. Warm welcome and seating on an enclosed terrace overlooking the green. The service was just ok. Professional but a little slower than we might have liked. Food and drink quality excellent although the ice cream was not as good as at the original. If weather is good, try and get a table on the first floor terrace but they are all ok. \u00a3100 for two drinks and three courses each was very fair value. We will be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r661157656", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Nibbles and drink", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "25 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MariolaAhaha", "reviewer_origin": ["Reykjavik, Iceland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "118"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "24"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r661157656-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I do like The Ivy, trained staff, great food and smiley faces, its very personal in comparison to other brands. Love the deco. This one reminds me of the one in Manchester which is also great. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r662489761", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely mothers day late lunch", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "31 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "AndrewR941", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "159"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "81"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r662489761-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Its obviously not the West End original but they've done an amazing job in a modernist box in the park in the middle of canary wharf ! The internal decor is familiar from Ivy restaurants, with lots of greenery and art deco art. The usual menu and fun bar: a martini to suit all tastes; we had a wide range of food from tempura shrimp,yellowfin tuna with wasabi mayo, and the for mains shepherds pie, roast chicken with truffle mash, and a monkfish and shrimp keralan curry - all delicious. washed down with a decent white wine, a couple of expresso martini's and a creme br\u00fbl\u00e9e. \u00a3200 all in with a decent wine for 3 of us - a lovely Sunday lunch."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r666117611", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Perfect from start to finish, birthday celebration!", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "13 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "876steveo", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "12"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r666117611-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We reserved a table for 4 this Saturday to celebrate a 33rd birthday. Our first step into this iconic building and i was greeted by the 3 friendly receptionists. The decor and ambiance is fantastic, nice touch with the DJ! We started with canopes and the signature g & ts! Fabulous. The mains followed which were equally as delicious and all served perfectly by Greg. He was courteous , polite and friendly. After dessert our hosts presented us with our birthday cake and digestive drinks. Well done team, keep up the good work. Overall a fantastic experience and we cant wait to return ."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r663288774", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Set lunch menu", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "2 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Wedding08_12", "reviewer_origin": ["Merthyr Tydfil, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "88"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "61"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r663288774-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Had the set menu at the Ivy. There was quite a lot to choose from. The portions were surprisinly quite generous and food was well presented. The service was good and staff were very friendly. The mains were all very nice and we all enjoyed. The desserts were delicious. Would definitely go back. Good value for money."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r664533736", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Good dinner for vegetarian and pescatarian ", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "7 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "NicholasK887", "reviewer_origin": ["Bridgetown, Barbados"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "337"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "129"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r664533736-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["A few of us worked all day on a booth at Excel and headed out to dinner right afterwards. We didn\u2019t have a reservation but managed to get a table right away. The service was very friendly. The seating is a quite comfortable and the menu quite extensive. The wine list is also quite extensive although a little pricey. ", "We had a vegetarian and pescatarian plus two meat eaters. All of us were very happy with the whole dinner. ", "The one slight flaw was that the smoke from the people smoking outside the front door was wafting in to our table all the time so we didn\u2019t enjoy that at all. But the food and company made up for it!!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r665847275", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Impeccable Staff/mediocre food", "diner_date": " April 2019", "rating_date": "13 April 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lizziegi", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r665847275-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Met here for drinks, having booked a table for supper. The staff were impeccable from the start. Quick to serve us with drinks, then to easily bring forward our supper reservation to a more convenient time for us.", "Upstairs in the dining area, the young waiter looking after our table was excellent. Professional, courteous and extremely helpful. ", "Now for the food.", "Once ordered, we waited quite a while for three cold starters and one scallops, which, were cold on reaching our table!", "It was rectified quickly though and the next plate was hot.", "I couldn\u2019t have my first choice of main as they had just sold the last one! (We were in early at seven o\u2019clock) so I opted for lamb. My mistake I suppose. Asked for medium but, in my opinion, the middle was almost raw. It was mentioned to the very kind waiter as he took our plates away. The other three meals were received and enjoyed.", "The scallops and lamb were removed from the bill, which wasn\u2019t asked for by any of our party. Top marks for that. ", "I would be inclined to try again here, definitely for drinks downstairs, and maybe on a night less busy? if this is at all possible in London? ", "For me personally, there are far better places to eat , but I\u2019m willing to hold my hand up and say it could have been the wrong choice on the night. ", "As mentioned though, the staff were faultless, and as a frequent visitor to this city, that means a lot."]}
