{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r659256034", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Late Lunch with my girls for a Bridal Celebration", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "18 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Lolaally", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r659256034-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Occasion: Pre-bridal celebration lunch for my best friend.", "I visited The Ivy in London Bridge last August for a friend's birthday lunch and the service was terrible. I wasn't too keen on the idea of eating at The Ivy again after that experience but my friends really wanted to go as they had never been, so I agreed to give it one last try. ", "I Just want to say a big THANK YOU to The Ivy Canary Wharf staff, in particular, Fillipo who looked after us the entire time while we were there and also Alex, the manager. They were both very welcoming, polite and kind. Honestly, the service overall was a 10/10 and me and the girls all agreed on this! ", "Thank you very much for the excellent service you provided Filipo and Alex!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r659936458", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing surroundings, Tasty food and Excellent service", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "20 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "NicolasSteven", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "3"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r659936458-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a warm greeting from the reception staff who took as to our table on the first floor, from which we had an extraordinary view of canary wharf. Our waitress Sabrina provided us with a high level of service, helping as with any queries we had. As the restaurant is located in canary wharf their are a lot of businesses guest meaning the atmosphere was peaceful and our waitress had the time to go the extra mile with us. Thank you so much for making our night. ", "P.s My favorite touch was still providing us with water after we had paid the bill at which point most people would stop looking after you but she truly looked after us from start to finish."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r659482089", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "everything cooked so well......", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "19 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "swpratt", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "639"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "233"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r659482089-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Met son Chris for an early evening meal after an interesting walk via the docklands museum and a little bit of tropical rain forest. Warmly welcomed and straight to a tablr overlooking the grassy square that reminded me a bit of union square in San Francisco.", "Had the appetisers rather than starters - what a great choice. Big bowl of matchstick thin utterly tasty zucchini fries with a dipping sauce, some lovely bread and some Moorish truffle aranchini - well enough for 3. ", "Chris had the roast chicken and he loved its crispy coating. My steak tartare was as good as I've had outside France. When will british restaurants allow us to mix it ourselves?", "Great meal, great service - will definitely go again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r654132029", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Business lunch", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "22 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mr_h_pinner", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "52"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "28"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r654132029-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Nice food. Lovely lager. Crab and salmon to start and a perfect medium cooked sirloin. Good value. 2 Nice bottle of wine at a reasonable price. Just shy of half a G for 7 people and a few lunchtime drinks. Waiters/esses are really helpful and nice. "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r658108440", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Not what I had expcted", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "12 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "simon p", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "145"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "43"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r658108440-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Great location and venue with excellent,professional friendly service but frankly the food was just not special. This is not fine dining but an upmarket chain. No specials, no real flair or anything different or exciting on the menu, which does not vary. For the money you could spend your cash more wisely."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r659824615", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Food consistently good, service consistently bad", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "20 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Jojobm", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "10", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r659824615-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I've been to this restuarant a number of times now and whilst the food is consisently good, the service is consistently bad. It's just so unnecessarily sloppy and it really lets this place down.", "Waiting staff don't seem particularly well briefed on any aspect of the menu, and the more senior staff just flit around without actually paying any attention to the needs of their guests. ", "As an example, each time I've been someone in my party has had to ask for wine to be topped up several times. Last night my party had to ask 5 times and also had to wave pretty frantically to get the attention of someone - anyone. The table next to us had a similar experience.", "The reality is that i'll probably go back as the food is good and the setting lovely but they really need to up their game service wise - it's not a patch on the original."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r655056878", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Lovely evening", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "26 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SusanS569", "reviewer_origin": ["Surrey, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "89"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r655056878-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the Ivy initially just for a drink and then decided to eat, we had not booked and so there were no tables left in the restaurant, we were however able to eat at our table in the bar. Good choice of cocktails and beer and a really good offer on food. Prices were reasonable and the food was delicious. Lovely d\u00e9cor and excellent service, would recommend."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r655107768", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Lovely ambience, but more attention needed on the food", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "26 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Londontripadviser", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "225"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "115"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "30"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r655107768-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["First the positives - it's clear a lot of money has been spent on the fit out of this restaurant. The layout and ambience (French retro-chic) are great and it's an enjoyable experience to eat here.", "Unfortunately, however, the food did not live up to expectations or the fit out. I had a cheese omelette and some toast on the side. The omelette was very over-cooked - picture the consistency of an executive stress toy - and the toast was very small and pretty uninspiring.", "That said, I'd still go back as I've had good experiences at other Ivys and I presume it was a one-off."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r655375748", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Locations differ significantly in quality of food", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "28 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Susannelcp20", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "40", "20"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r655375748-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I recently went to The Ivy in Blackheath and then again yesterday in Canary Wharf. Whilst the food was excellent and tasty and fresh in the Blackheath location, the food was of poor quality and tasteless in Canary Wharf which was rather disappointing. ", "The setting and design is great in both locations. ", "I would love to go back to the Blackheath location but probably find another alternative Restaurant in Canary wharf."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r656510141", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "A special lunch with friends on a Saturday", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "5 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "diner212015", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "12"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r656510141-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The location of the Ivy in the Park in Canary Wharf is fantastic with outside seating too. The menu is great and reasonably priced and the bar is luxurious. Food is good and there's a good cocktail and wine list. There's a good 'buzz' in the restaurant and bar and the staff are helpful and attentive. I've already booked again for March."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r655692277", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Breakfast for a queen", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "1 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Nicole F", "reviewer_origin": ["Orpington, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "35"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "23"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r655692277-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Ambience in this place was amazing it was so relaxing.", "I had breakfast with friends. I had scrambled eggs and lobster and it was huge. I never had lunch because it was so filling. My friends had scrambled eggs and salmon and the other had an English breakfast and we was all satisfied.", "I paid \u00a320 for my breakfast which is actually quite expensive but as I don\u2019t do it everyday I don\u2019t mind. I will certainly be going it again."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r655437681", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Saturday night out ", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "28 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "thornekevin2", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "54"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "18"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r655437681-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had an excellent dinner with our friends here the other Saturday night and it was well worth it the food & service was very good they even had a DJ playing some nice tunes not to loud as well "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r657800412", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Best Gourmet deluxe In Canary Wharf ", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "11 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "blajevaina", "reviewer_origin": ["Berlin, Germany"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "118"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "160"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r657800412-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This Place is mesmerising inside out . The actual sustainable building is piece of art itself and inside is amazing colonial gardens style deluxe . Very easy to access from everywhere you can missed it the only lower building in Canada Place Gardens standing alone amongst the skyscrapers around . Best parking solution is under Waitrose and you\u2019ll get the 3 hours free when for \u00a310 spend but you need to verify you parking tickets at the Waitrose till until 9 pm . The atmosphere in Ivy is always good vibes and luxurious because of the many plants all around and many vintage decorations it feels so posh but cozy. The balconies with the lush green all around and the second floor are spectacular. The views around are 180 of skyscrapers and you can miss the beauty of it in the evenings or daytime .", "We when there twice since they opened for lunch and dinner now we plan for Sunday breakfast brunch on the balconies!", "The food is one of the best in town and for Canary Wharf is my Top 1 ! ", "Portions are bigger then all other posh restaurant ! everything is absolutely delicious all the meals are with fancy presentation but easy to eat and enjoy. ", "We love the chicken dishes and the fish dishes. All the salads and vegetarian options are delicious too . It\u2019s easy to taste the proper organic ingredients and top quality special produce ! ", "Wine list is amazing very big selection very special wines. Cocktails are delish classics with a twist which you will not get anywhere else. We love the Cosmo and Margaritas which sounds old fashion but they have put a spin on it and taste amazing! ", "Service and staff are the Best in Canary Wharf! Top professionals superb trained and so efficient in what they do that is absolute pleasure to be served by so friendly fast thinking beautifully people ! ", "Prices \u00a3\u00a3 are the usual for this kind of place but totally good value for money ! ", "Best place for any kind of celebrations and occasions ! ", "Good for Brunches much with the children especially in the garden when the weather is good ! ", "Go enjoy and make a happy memories \u2764\ufe0f", "You\u2019ll get more then you expected for sure! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r657853021", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fabulous on every level!", "diner_date": " March 2019", "rating_date": "11 March 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Susan B", "reviewer_origin": ["Reykjavik, Iceland"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r657853021-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Just celebrated birthday lunch here today - we are 2 women in our 60\u2019s - the service couldn\u2019t have been better - incredibly welcoming, lovely table and very informative and friendly. The food was just great - we shared a huge portion of crispy fried courgettes with the house gin and tonic - perfect - I had chicken Milanese with Parmesan/truffle chips (ny partner had duck salad - main course portion), we shared chocolate bombe (beautifully served) - everything was just delicious........ the decor was gorgeous, the bill was good value - what\u2019s not to like? We weill be back and recommending to all our friends - thank you so much to everyone at Canary Wharf for making our lunch truly memorable"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r651299520", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Nice dinner", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "10 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "sanou65", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "34"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "1"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r651299520-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I called to book in the morning they said it fully booked ! We said let\u2019s try our chance and go ! When we went we found a table I don\u2019t understand why they have said no in the morning! ", "The food was nice and the atmosphere as well ! The desert wasn\u2019t that great! The bombe chocolat was too hard to break! ", "Hope next time will be better ! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r654064075", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "1", "title": "worst restaurant iv ever been to", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "22 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "JingJing21", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["10", "10", "10"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r654064075-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["firstly we went there for breakfast to start my birthday celebration. when we arrived at the restaurant they tell us that fried eggs will not be available so ok fine. we chose our food and after 10 minutes they tell us they are having problems with their gas so they are not able to give us what we ordered so we have to order something else. few minutes later they said that's not available as well by this time my kids and myself and hubby are starving. they basically ruined what was meant to be a special day for the family and although they have not charged us for the food and made me pay for the drinks is ridiculous. I went there intending to eat good food and treat the family for my birthday not to have just drinks. if they would have been honest from the beginning and told us the truth we would have gone somewhere else to eat and not have our day ruined and made us pay for service we didn't want in the first place. we were conned into staying there to spend money and waste time that was suppose to be spent happily with my family.!!! Its the most ridiculous place and worst customer service iv ever been to in my life never ever going back there ever"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r651778348", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "One of best in east London / Canary Wharf for brunch ", "diner_date": " February 2019", "rating_date": "12 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Pulaq P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "18"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "5"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r651778348-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Finally an awesome place for brunch in this area .. great food and cozy ambience . ", "Been here few times now and have taken friends .. we all loved it . ", "Ordered egg royal , truffle chicken sandwich , halloumi sandwich and pancake .. all was great "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r651479518", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fantastic lunch!", "diner_date": " January 2019", "rating_date": "11 February 2019", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ClareMcK", "reviewer_origin": ["Burnham-on-Crouch, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "411"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "171"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r651479518-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We booked before Christmas for a January lunch reservation. I would highly recommend that you check for availability as I saw people being turned away.", "The menu was varied and there were dishes for all dietary requirements. The staff were fantastic and were on hand to help with any queries.", "I opted for the Vegan menu and the dishes all looked tempting. I think next time, I may choose a fish dish as they looked so tempting.", "My colleagues and I spent around 90 minutes at the restaurant. A colleague ordered the Apple Tatin which took 15 minutes to arrive and looked amazing. The chocolate Bombes were pretty cool; a bit of theatre for Instagram!", "Sitting outside when it's a bit warmer would be lovely too. I highly recommend this restaurant to you and know I will be back very soon."]}
