{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r638967929", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Highly recommend ", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "722evieh", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "20"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "21"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r638967929-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I visited the Ivy in the park this evening for dinner with my mum as part of an early Xmas gift.", "The decor is beautiful, we were sat upstairs overlooking the ice rink. The service was outstanding.", "We both had a classic champagne cocktail.", "For starters the duck and watermelon dish- beautiful.", "Mains the shepherds pie and the shoulder of lamb with green beans and wilted spinach.", "I could have eaten more of the Sheppard\u2019s pie ifs the portion was bigger. ", "For desert we had the creme br\u00fbl\u00e9e and the rum baba.", "The atmosphere and food were equally great. I would advise you to book ahead as it is very popular.", "5/5! "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r639180574", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Home from home, very close to O2 and City", "diner_date": " December 2018", "rating_date": "12 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "jandrewsesq", "reviewer_origin": ["Leigh-on Sea, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "114"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "74"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r639180574-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["As with every Ivy off shoot, this branch carries the same menu and similar decor to the original in West Street so you always know what you're going to get. You can eat expensive, or inexpensive depending on your pocket on the day, but one thing's for certain...you'll always have a phenomenal meal.", "The staff here are awesome, and the atmosphere great too. ", "We ate late for lunch and early for dinner, then walked to the station and rode for one stop to the O2. What a perfect way to start the evening, with perfect food and perfect wine....thank you Ivy"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r633907020", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "A great addition to Canary Wharf.........", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "17 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ajp9000", "reviewer_origin": ["Royal Tunbridge Wells, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "133"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "78"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["40", "40", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r633907020-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["My first visit to the Ivy in Canary Wharf which has been open for around a month now. In may other locations the Ivy would just be another restaurant generally in the top quartile, but in Canary Wharf it is easily in the top three. Many of the restaurants in Canary Wharf are a disappointment being soul less, average quality at best, and poor value, but the Ivy does raise the standard with a good location, generally good service, but could be better which hopefully will come as they get established. Could not complain about the food and wine all in line with other Ivy's, so will certainly be returning on a regular basis."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r638979044", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Superb", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "11 December 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "SimoneLucia", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "22"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r638979044-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Upon my arrival into the restaurant the service received was warm, welcoming, accommodating and very professional. ", "A wide option of choice for drinks: Jamaican Wray & Nephew white rum was there. The food was delicious ", "Overall: a humbling experience ", "I would like to use this opportunity to say Thank you to the staff for providing an wonderful experience "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r636745940", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Fab place for quality and GOOD pastry", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "30 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "WML7613", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r636745940-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This was our second time at the Ivy. We just had dinner there and the food was as good as their afternoon tea. ", "We had prawn tempura as starters which had a different take from the traditional Japanese tempura. ", "The main course, Lobster linguine was light and tasty and lastly the apple tart was superb especially if you like it with an after taste of alcohol as they set it on fire at the table, like you do on a Christmas cake. ", "As it was a birthday booking, I was given a little birthday pastry with a little candle and a piece of chocolate that said Happy Birthday. ", "We we well looked after by the waitress and Valerio whom we remembered from our first visit. Looking forward to our next meal there with the children."]}
