{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r635681207", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Another Ivy restaurant", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "25 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "mrsGiroud", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "290"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "111"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r635681207-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was very excited to see the Ivy being built in Canary Wharf and eventually we managed a lunch booking last week. Was surprised how busy it was even though we got there early. However service was good and our food and drinks came quickly. Our server was very pleasant and didn't pressure us when we took our time ordering", "We did have one issue when our 2nd round of drinks didn't turn up. But a manager came by to apologise and offered complimentary chocolate truffles. ", "Cocktails are good. Food has plenty of options and not that pricey! ", "Will definitely be back "]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r635459708", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "It was like a Cliff Richard concert with good food.", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "24 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Indimenticabile", "reviewer_origin": ["Richmond, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "109"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "47"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "50", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r635459708-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Was taken there after a meeting recently and having heard of, but never eaten in any of the Ivy chain, I was looking forward to the occasion. ", "The restaurant is bright, in places, with a nice buzz. The service was good, attentive without being intrusive. Wines can be pricey if you have the budget.", "The food was good. I had smoked salmon with crab, followed by sea bass. Some of the others had steak which was well received. The side dishes, which are essential, were ok.", "The Cliff Richard comment? We were allocated to a table in the part which has \u201civy\u201d on the ceiling and it was so dark that we had to use our phones as torches to be able to read the menu. There were a few lamps, not on all tables, but the lighting is just not acceptable in that part. So specify that you want to be seated elsewhere unless it is daylight!"]}
