{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r635645081", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "4", "title": "Excellent food and drinks but slow service.", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "25 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "josiek166", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "7"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "10"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r635645081-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I\u2019ve visited the Ivy on Old Broad Street and at One Tower Bridge and last night (Saturday) I visited the Canary Wharf Branch. The atmosphere and food was lovely, I had the steak which was definitely 10/10 and was much better than I expected. The wine was quite expensive per glass but very enjoyable along with the dessert which was delicious- I had the chocolate bomb.", "My only complaint is that the service is very slow! We had to get the waiters attention to order drinks and again when it came to paying. ", "We will be returning but hope to see the service improve."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r633627118", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Will be good when they get the service sorted", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "15 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "rcspeirs", "reviewer_origin": ["London"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "68"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "20"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["30", "20", "40"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r633627118-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["This should be a great addition to the choice in Canary Wharf - when the staff are bedded in and things run smoothly. Our visit was just a couple of weeks after opening and service was very much an issue. Our aperitifs only arrived after a very long wait - I had to stop a passing manager to get that sorted. The food was great - simple classics done well.", "Nice decor but at some tables the lighting level is so low you need to use the torch function in your battery to be able to read the menu."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r631745545", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great for date night", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "7 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "ENTOURAGE_10", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "36"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r631745545-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We had a lovely evening, lovely food, scallops to start were epic! The venue is beautiful, the attention to detail wonderful, love all the linen, the lighting. There was a DJ on when we were in, playing some great tunes, really added to atmosphere and helped the wonderful cosmos keep flowing, love the glassware by the way. There were plenty of staff, and were friendly and enjoying themselves, was nice to see the management supporting obviously new team members find their feet. Our waiter Igor was extremely pleasant and knew the menu and guided us through. Great job."]}
