{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r631578213", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Great dinner in a beautiful set-up!", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "7 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "meliob2016", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "4"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "4"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r631578213-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["In a few words: My friend and I had a trully exceptional experience at the Ivy in The Park last week. I would highly recommend this restaurant and we will be definitely coming back here ourselves very soon.", "To begin with, we were warmly greeted and felt welcome from the very first second we set our foot in - which is no longer the case in many restaurants in London...", "We were shown to our table and our waitress, Lavignia, who was so sweet and polite, took the time to explain the menu, inform us about what was unavailable and make suggestions based on our preferences.", "Starters: we shared the foie gras and the crispy duck salad between the two of us and both were delicious!! The foie gras was served on a brioche toast with roasted apples and was so juicy and yummy, I cannot even describe... as for the duck salad - well we could both have more and more of it, the freshness of the watermelon in combination with the crispiness of the duck and the taste of the hoisin sauce was so refreshing and almost addictive. Both starters are a no-miss for anyone who visits!", "Mains: I had the monkfish and prawn curry which came with jasmine rice on the side and was one of the best I've had. The monkfish was a tiny bit chewy but that's very often the case with monkfish so I didn't mind at all. Overall it was a hearty dish, very fragrant and just a bit spicy - just the way I like it, so extremely happy with my choice - which was our waitress suggestion btw.", "Here I need to mention that the whole team was very attentive, fast and polite in their interactions with us. Alex, I think he is the manager, even came to personally check upon us and make sure we were happy with everything and get our feedback.", "Also, you need to pay a visit to the restrooms, as they are beautifully designed (...and highly instagrammable)!", "To sum up: we were both SO happy with our time here! Thank you for taking care of us, we will be back very soon for more!"]}
