{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630418647", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing food and service, highly recommend!", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Umang_RAJ_1994", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "2"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "3"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630418647-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We went to the restaurant for both dinner and brunch, the service we received was incredibly polite and quick. The food was lovely on both occasions! The decor of their new location is amazing and the views from upstairs is great, makes the experience even better."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630421805", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Amazing Restaurant, Amazing Service, Delicious Food and Perfect Cocktails", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Kamilla P", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630421805-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["We visited the restaurant for my sister's birthday. The restaurant is in a beautiful building with the most amazing decorations outside and inside. The staff was very friendly, helpful and efficient from the time we arrived at the restaurant. Before we sat down to our table we went to the bar where we got serve fast even though the restaurant was already very busy. The bar staff was very helpful to explain and recommend cocktails, just like the waiting staff who even though were busy they took the time to explain and recommend dishes. The service was fast and efficient and the food arrived promptly. Everything we had was amazingly delicious. At the end of the meal, we even got a small but delicious cake and a Happy Birthday song for my sister which made the experience even better. I would definitely recommend this restaurant, and we will be back!"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630491338", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "2 for dinner ", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "YogiShar", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "8"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630491338-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["It really was a tale of 2 halves.", "We arrived an hour early and were greeted by a really lovely lady who found us a table for drinks. We opted for the salted caramel espresso martini and a table for 2 opposite the bar and close to the dj.", "Great ambience, interesting decor and a plethora of happy smiling staff.", "When our table was ready we were guided upstairs to our table with views of Plateau in one direction and the Ice Rink in the other. Quite a busy night upstairs and we instantly noticed there were a lot less staff there.", "The manager Valerio was very attentive, spoke passionately about The Ivy,, guided us through the popular choices on the menu and we felt in safe hands.", "From this point forward the food and service were hit and miss.", "We had a second set of drinks and some water and ordered our food and my friend ordered a glass of wine.", "To start we had the courgette which was julienned and battered and served like matchstick chips in a basket and wooden tongs. Absolutely delicious. The sauce it came with was far too acidic but tolerable in small amounts. The scallops ( we were assured there were 6 in a portion), appeared about table as a portion of 2 on top of a weird sauce and very very undercooked inedible butternut squash. This was not a good dish!", "For mains we has the Shepherds Pie which smelt comforting and rich and looked as yummy as it tasted.", "The lamb shoulder was one of the most depressing mains I have had this year. The veg carrots and parsnips were lukewarm and undercooked again. The lamb itself had a eye wateringly strong and sour wasabi smeared thickly on top. The first bite was interesting the subsequent mouthful were a mistake.", "We really didn't fancy dessert after that. Valerio knew we weren't happy and offered us a post dinner drink or dessert but the disappointing savoury courses didnt entice us to stay longer.", "I had such high hopes and am hoping that the kitchen just had an off day. I will go back as it is welcome relief to have somewhere new to go for a dinner treat and fingers crossed that dinner will be everything that other reviewers say."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630505287", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Beautiful new restaurant with efficient friendly service and outstanding food", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Paul D", "reviewer_origin": ["Torquay, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "147"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "30"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630505287-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["The ivy on the park has a great atmosphere and for such a new restaurant the service and food is amazing. It is in the centre Of Canary Wharf and should not be missed. We sat upstairs which was lovely."]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630584913", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "Wonderful family dinner , great service ", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "3 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "95lilianaa", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630584913-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Second time I\u2019ve visit this amazing venue, this time with my teenage boys .", "I was surprised with their compliments regarding decor and food , they loved the Fish and chips and the Burger .", "This time my wife had Lobster and Prawn Cocktail followed by Lobster Linguini as it\u2019s her favourite dish .", "I tried the Foie gras followed by Ribeye steak , Foie gras was great and ribeye was one of the best ever .", "Overall just to say thanks , can\u2019t wait to be back !"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630781076", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "2", "title": "Brunch- was not impressed at all", "diner_date": " November 2018", "rating_date": "4 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "301yuliag", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "33"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "17"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630781076-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["I came for brunch with my friend on Sunday. Very limited choices for brunch, plus opinionated manager who decided that she knows better how i should have my food. Overall very average food and which is a shame as we were all waiting for the launch with excitement..not a good start.. hopefully that will change"]}
{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r630711218", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "3", "title": "Average food, middling service ", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "4 November 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "MirHayes", "reviewer_origin": ["London, United Kingdom"], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "44"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "68"]], "other_ratings_category": [], "other_ratings_value": [], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r630711218-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Visited with a couple of friends for Sunday brunch. We all opted for eggs benedict / eggs royale with chips. ", "The eggs were well cooked but not very hot, the hollandaise was flavourless and the chips were luke-warm. The ham was tasty and fresh. ", "We placed a second order for truffle-parmesan chips, which were hot and delicious. ", "There seems to a weird food transfer / holding pattern where the food is brought out from the kitchen, taken through to a crockery dresser where it sits on the tray and waits to be taken to the table. We noticed our food sitting there for 5 minutes before someone brought it over to us.", "We skipped dessert and asked for the bill from a waitress who forgot. 15 minutes later I got the attention of the ma\u00eetre d' who returned promptly with our bill. ", "All in all a reasonable brunch, not brilliant, but not terrible. Hopefully with time these small issues will be resolved. "]}
