{"id_resto": "g186338-d15238588", "id_comment": "g186338-d15238588-r629696330", "resto": "The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf", "resto_url": "/Restaurant_Review-g186338-d15238588-Reviews-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "rating": "5", "title": "First Class", "diner_date": " October 2018", "rating_date": "30 October 2018", "answer_text": null, "reviewer_pseudo": "Odyssey51282718862", "reviewer_origin": [], "reviewer_info_sup": [["pencil-paper", "1"], ["thumbs-up-fill", "2"]], "other_ratings_category": ["Value", "Service", "Food"], "other_ratings_value": ["50", "50", "50"], "url": "https://www.tripadvisor.co.uk/ShowUserReviews-g186338-d15238588-r629696330-The_Ivy_Canary_Wharf-London_England.html", "content": ["Thank you so much for what I can only describe as an absolutely great dining experience at The Ivy in the Park. ", "You and your staff were so accommodating upon arrival at reception (despite being so busy, they were able to robustly offer a table change - for a good view of course!) and my friend and I instantly felt relaxed about what the rest of the night was to bring. ", "The dishes were very very tasty, I almost felt like I was in a different part of the world, I cheekily did make a top-up request on something in particular from your menu. I will keep that to myself, haha!", "My friend had a wonderful time and liked that she could order surprise requests on cocktails from the bartender - she sure loved those surprises. Also if you wouldn\u2019t mind telling me how you got those mouth-watering olives so juicy, I would like to try making some for friends and family since I enjoyed it so much. ", "I am already making further dinner arrangements at your restaurant, so sorry if I become a regular, haha.", "What an impeccable knowledge of the overall menu from your waiter - Jana. She was able to recommend the most beautiful cocktails and dishes - based on what I said I liked to eat - delicious! ", "The dessert I had was absolutely \"bomb\" ...bursting with nothing but sweet things in my mouth. My friend enjoyed her dessert as well. I know she will remember the evening for some time!", "Thank you also for having the patience and not rushing us with the food and drinks all at once the timing between courses were all good.", "It was so nice to know we didn\u2019t have to worry as much about our food and whilst we were there, and that we were able to order it in time when we were ready.", "Once again THANK YOU SO MUCH for everything! We had a great overall experience, you and your staff, - Patricia, Jana, Antonio and the senior members of staff that took their time to even introduce themselves, you all contributed to making it that way! ", "I will definitely be back very soon! I\u2019ll be sure to let you know in advance before I return with friends and family.", "Thanks again for all your hard work and consideration.", "CeeJai O."]}
